# Divine Strategist Abilities
Domains	KEY:Domains ~ Divine Strategist	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality	BONUS:DOMAIN|NUMBER|-1	DESC:A divine strategist gains only a single domain.	
Master Tactician	KEY:Master Tactician ~ Divine Strategist	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality	DESC:A divine strategist can use the aid another action to assist another divine spellcaster, granting a +%1 circumstance bonus on caster level checks and concentration checks until the beginning of the divine strategist's next turn. The allied caster must remain adjacent to the divine strategist to gain this benefit. Caster support can be used to assist arcane spellcasters or characters using magical items, but they gain only half the normal bonus.|2+classlevel("Cleric")/4
Tactical Expertise	KEY:Tactical Expertise ~ Divine Strategist	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality	DESC:A divine strategist knows how to take best advantage of tactical opportunities. Whenever she is flanking or makes an attack of opportunity, she may add her Intelligence bonus (if any) as a bonus on the attack roll. In addition, %1 times per day as a swift action she may add her Intelligence modifier as a bonus on any single d20 roll made as part of a readied action.|1+(MAX(0,classlevel("Cleric")-8)/2)

